  <releases>
    <release version="0.6.0" date="2021-09-18">
      <description>
        <ul>
          <li>Added support for equations of the form x = f(y);</li>
          <li>Added support for polar equations of the forms r = f(θ) and θ = f(r);</li>
          <li>Added support for custom logarithm bases;</li>
          <li>Added animations to zooming;</li>
          <li>Refined the grid appearance, and added grid labels;</li>
          <li>Added French and Dutch translations;</li>
          <li>Minor bug fixes.</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
